data.description: Beautiful four bedroom, three bathroom Avondale home!! Soaring ceilings, stunning wood looking tile, and a fresh coat of clean neutral paint greet you as you enter through the front door. The fully remodeled kitchen is great for entertaining with an abundance of refreshing white cabinetry, quartz counters, stainless steel appliances, and plenty of space!! All of the bedrooms are generously sized. The master suite boasts vaulted ceilings, ample room, and a luxurious full ensuite with updates!  The backyard offers a large refreshing pool and covered patio with new overhang! This home is going to go fast,  so come take a look today!
